title: Upper Corner Apt+New Kitchen+ Wood Floors, Lakes Maka Ska, Harriet
map_address: Emerson Ave S near 36th St W
posting_body: ['One bedroom/one bath apartment with many windows in upper front corner of classic brick brownstone just 6 blocks to lake Bde Maka Ska, 1 block to quiet path along Kings Highway, 6 blocks to gardens at Lake Harriet, South Uptown neighborhood.', 'Well-maintained building with on-site caretaker and local owner.', 'Features: NEW KITCHEN--including new appliances, granite counters, new cabinets, dishwasher and microwave.', 'HARDWOOD FLOORS through-out this corner apartment.', 'Good daylight with EIGHT newer windows including full screens for easy operation and excellent ventilation and window blinds.', 'Full living room, dining room, bedroom, and ceramic tile bath.', 'Common area offers newer laundry, INDOOR BIKE STORAGE, and storage lockers.', 'CONVENIENT LAKES LOCATION: 6 blocks to Lake Bde Maka Ska (Calhoun), 1 block to shady trail along Kings Highway, 6 blocks to gardens at Lake Harriet.', 'Close to bus stops on Hennepin, Bryant, and West 36th St.', 'TERMS:', 'Rent is based one-person occupancy.', 'Two-person maximum; additional monthly rent for second person.', 'Rent includes heat, water, sewer and household trash.', 'Resident pays monthly electricity and cooking gas.', "Damage deposit equal to one month's rent due at lease signing.", "Full first month's rent due when you move in.", 'Application fee: $30/adult.', 'No smoking.', 'One off-street parking space available for additional monthly rent.', 'One cat o.k. with payment $20 per month pet rent.', 'Sorry, dogs are not allowed.', 'When you reply by email, please tell us: 1.', 'how many adults and children; 2.', 'whether anyone smoke; 3.', 'whether you have any animals or pets; 4. preferred move-in date; 5.', 'your telephone number and email address.', 'Thank you.']
